{"tid":138634,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌","createTime":"2017-02-28T17:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T05:28:21.000Z","uid":14170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c4105d3d3bbee5460b3dade1ab99617425f1fc","tid":138634,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:44:57.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌。<br />\n就職後要拼盡全力賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港城市大學 LLB 進場，先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿 PCLL，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功 KO 第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4 年 Company Law，將來就可以用法律監管政府各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫政府和中國，美國聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為香港制定未來政策。 <br />\n表現好的話可以入人大。 <br />\n簡直是世界主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"1e6a48b0f2e0d9490b0727762d707b94ec918d47","tid":138634,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:47:47.000Z","msg":"咪loop"},{"pid":"20457292b74af0b206160b5606d3874cd117e519","tid":138634,"uid":77138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:51:55.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"128a4f5e1bbd7273e28cea65becf40d5424918f1","tid":138634,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T19:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f567b6a109776a54e88ec8331832cce1b83d1c3","tid":138634,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T19:12:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5421c308d84b1ba0e2b184a9249d49716f7590de","tid":138634,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:22:54.000Z","msg":"Ou都出黎打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef15d5b761c58aad7e263f777d088afce1246e17","tid":138634,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ou都出黎打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lom